# Upstash Redis (required for online multiplayer on Vercel).
# Create a free database at https://upstash.com or add the "Upstash" integration
# from the Vercel Marketplace (Storage tab) — it injects these automatically.
#
# Either of these env var name pairs works:
KV_REST_API_URL=
KV_REST_API_TOKEN=

# (alternative names also supported)
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
#
# If none are set, the app falls back to an in-memory store. That works for
# `npm run dev` on a single machine, but NOT on Vercel (serverless functions
# don't share memory) — so set these before deploying.
